com.google.gwt.file.client

Class Blob

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • com.google.gwt.file.client.Blob
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    File

    public class Blob
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    This class represents raw data. It provides a method to slice data objects between ranges of bytes into further chunks of raw data. It also provides an attribute representing the size of the chunk of data. The File interface inherits from this interface.

    See http://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/FileAPI/#dfn-Blob
